    b"\x0d\x0a        Prepare the input text that will be stitched under the selected task\x0d\x0a"
    b"        prompt before it is sent to the selected task.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Return compact"
    b" task_input text from the supplied context.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Guidance:\x0d\x0a        - Buil"
